<HEADLINE>
<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"It's hard to believe that 40 pounds of muchacho could cause $275,000 of 
damage, but there it is." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Los Angeles Police Detective Ben Lovato, after two boys -- one 9 years old, 
the other 8 -- were arrested on suspicion of starting a fire that caused an 
estimated $275,000 damage to their Boyle Heights school, forcing officials to 
cram six classes into the auditorium and other temporary quarters. 
</P>
