Pro-life demonstrators should be honored that the lawyers for the American 
Civil Liberties Union are so enthusiastically persecuting them ("$5,000 Fines 
Urged in Abortion Protest," Metro, April 25). 
</P>
<P>
If the ACLU, known for embracing criminals' rights and defending Nazi marchers, 
