<P>
Photo, Detroit's Rick Mahorn (left) takes matters into his own hands, slinging 
Boston's Reggie Lewis over his back as Robert Parish comes to his Lewis' aid. 
Mahorn was charged with a technical. United Press International 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
