four strikeouts for host Mission Viejo (13-7, 4-2), which scored four runs in 
the second. Kerry McDaniels had three hits and an RBI. 
</P>
<P>
Irvine 4, El Toro 0 -- Jennifer Brundage (13-6) pitched a two-hitter, striking 
out six, for the Vaqueros (14-6, 5-1) at Irvine. Brundage also hit a two-run 
homer in the fourth. 
</P>
