host Tustin (12-7, 9-2), which clinched at least second place with two games 
left. Shannon Ellis tripled with the bases loaded to score three for University 
in the second. Ellis had four RBIs. Tustin trails first-place Saddleback by two 
games, but the teams play twice next week. 
</P>
