<HEADLINE>
<P>
POWER, THE NEWPORT BEACH ARTS COMMISSION, CENSORSHIP AND THE FULL NAKEDNESS OF 
ADAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I am writing with regard to the shabby and disrespectful treatment of Rosa 
Williamson's artwork at the Newport Beach City Hall Gallery. 
</P>
<P>
If people are offended by the subject matter of her paintings, the rational and 
adult solution is simply not to look at them. 
</P>
<P>
